'''花生四烯乙醇胺'''，亦稱'''N-花生四烯乙醇胺'''或'''AEA'''，是一種內源性的大麻醇類[[神經傳導物質|神經傳導物質]]。此命名取自[[梵文|梵文]]（和[[印度半島|印度半島]]宗教用語）的「[[阿難陀|阿難陀]]（ananda）」，意为「喜悅、極樂、欣喜」，以及[[醯胺|醯胺]]<ref name="pmid1470919">{{cite journal |last1=Devane|first1=W.|last2=Hanus|first2=L|last3=Breuer|first3=A|last4=Pertwee|first4=R.|last5=Stevenson|first5=L.|last6=Griffin|first6=G|last7=Gibson|first7=D|last8=Mandelbaum|first8=A|last9=Etinger|first9=A|last10=Mechoulam|first10=R|title=Isolation and structure of a brain constituent that binds to the cannabinoid receptor|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_science_1992-12-18_258_5090/page/1946|journal=Science|date=18 December 1992|volume=258|issue=5090|pages=1946–1949|doi=10.1126/science.1470919}}</ref><ref name="isbn0-12-551460-3">{{cite book |author= Mechoulam R, Fride E |editor=Pertwee RG |title=Cannabinoid receptors |url= https://archive.org/details/cannabinoidrecep0000unse |publisher=Academic Press |location=Boston |year=1995 |origyear= |pages=[https://archive.org/details/cannabinoidrecep0000unse/page/233 233]–258 |chapter=The unpaved road to the endogenous brain cannabinoid ligands, the anandamides |ISBN = 0-12-551460-3 }}</ref>。它是由N-花生四烯酰磷脂酰乙醇胺透過多種途徑合成<ref name=wang2009>{{cite journal | last=Wang | first=Jun | last2=Ueda | first2=Natsuo | title=Biology of endocannabinoid synthesis system | journal=Prostaglandins & Other Lipid Mediators | publisher=Elsevier BV | volume=89 | issue=3-4 | year=2009 | issn=1098-8823 | doi=10.1016/j.prostaglandins.2008.12.002 | pages=112–119}}</ref>。花生四烯乙醇胺，主要是由[[脂肪酸醯胺水解酶|脂肪酸醯胺水解酶]](FAAH)將其[[降解|降解]]成[[乙醇胺|乙醇胺]]和[[花生四烯酸|花生四烯酸]]。如此，[[脂肪酸醯胺水解酶|脂肪酸醯胺水解酶]](FAAH)的抑制物導致花生四烯乙醇胺層級的提升，並被用于治療<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Gaetani|first1=Silvana|last2=Dipasquale|first2=Pasqua|last3=Romano|first3=Adele|last4=Righetti|first4=Laura|last5=Cassano|first5=Tommaso|last6=Piomelli|first6=Daniele|last7=Cuomo|first7=Vincenzo|title=The endocannabinoid system as a target for novel anxiolytic and antidepressant drugs.|journal=International review of neurobiology|date=2009|volume=85|pages=57-72|doi=10.1016/S0074-7742(09)85005-8|pmid=19607961}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Hwang|first1=Jeannie|last2=Adamson|first2=Crista|last3=Butler|first3=David|last4=Janero|first4=David R.|last5=Makriyannis|first5=Alexandros|last6=Bahr|first6=Ben A.|title=Enhancement of endocannabinoid signaling by fatty acid amide hydrolase inhibition: A neuroprotective therapeutic modality|journal=Life Sciences|date=April 2010|volume=86|issue=15-16|pages=615–623|doi=10.1016/j.lfs.2009.06.003}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
其結構最初是由W. A. Devane, Lumír Hanuš等人在1992年時描述。當時他們在[[耶路撒冷|耶路撒冷]]的[[希伯來大學|希伯來大學]]一個由Raphael Mechoulam帶領的團隊工作。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Mechoulam |first=WA |author2=Hanus L |author3=Breuer A |author4=Pertwee RG |author5=Stevenson LA |author6=Griffin G |author7=Gibson D |author8=Mandelbaum A |author9=Etinger A |author10=Mechoulam R |title=Isolation and structure of a brain constituent that binds to the cannabinoid receptor |journal=Science |date=December 1992 |volume=258 |issue=5090 |pages=1946–9 |url=http://www.sciencemag.org/content/258/5090/1946.long |bibcode=1992Sci...258.1946D |doi=10.1126/science.1470919 |pmid=1470919 |access-date=2015-01-18 |archive-date=2014-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810034728/http://www.sciencemag.org/content/258/5090/1946.long |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 生理功能 ==
花生四烯乙醇胺可以作用在身體的[[中樞|中樞]]，例如[[腦部|腦部]]或其周邊；也可以作用在身體的其他部位。這些不同的作用主要是由[[CB1大麻素受體|CB1大麻素受體]]在[[中樞神經系統|中樞神經系統]]中調節，以及在[[周圍神經|周圍神經]]的[[CB2大麻素受體|CB2大麻素受體]]調控。<ref name="pmid16968947">{{cite journal | last=Pacher | first=P. | title=The Endocannabinoid System as an Emerging Target of Pharmacotherapy | journal=Pharmacological Reviews | publisher=American Society for Pharmacology & Experimental Therapeutics (ASPET) | volume=58 | issue=3 | date=2006-09-01 | issn=0031-6997 | doi=10.1124/pr.58.3.2 | pages=389–462}}</ref>後者主要參與[[免疫系統|免疫系統]]的功能作用。大麻素受體最初被發現時，被視為對[[四氫大麻酚|Δ<sup>9</sup>-四氫大麻酚]]（Δ<sup>9</sup>-THC，通常稱為THC）是敏感的，而其中THC是[[大麻|大麻]]中的主要精神活性物質。大麻素的發現源自於對CB1和CB2的研究，因為這是一個無可避免的內源性化學物質，並且會影響這些受體。花生四烯乙醇胺已經被證實會影響[[實驗大鼠|大鼠]]的工作記憶。<ref>{{cite journal |author= allet PE, Beninger RJ |title= The endogenous cannabinoid receptor agonist anandamide impairs memory in rats |url= http://www.behaviouralpharm.com/pt/re/bpharm/abstract.00008877-199605000-00008.htm |year= 1996 |journal= Behavioural Pharmacology |pages= 276–284 |volume= 7 |issue= 3 |doi= 10.1097/00008877-199605000-00008 |last2= Beninger |access-date= 2015-01-18 |archive-date= 2019-12-09 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191209040520/http://www.behaviouralpharm.com/pt/re/bpharm/abstract.00008877-199605000-00008.htm |dead-url= no }}</ref>而現在的研究正在探討大麻素作用對人類行為的影響，例如：在進食和睡眠的模式，以及疼痛減輕。花生四烯乙醇胺也對早期[[胚胎|胚胎]]中，[[妊娠|胚囊著床在子宮]]時有重要影響。因此大麻素，例如：Δ<sup>9</sup>-THC，可能在人類妊娠的早期階段影響其過程。<ref name="pmid14702623">{{cite journal |author= Piomelli D |title= THC: moderation during implantation |journal= Nat. Med. |volume= 10 |issue= 1 |pages= 19–20 |date=January 2004 |pmid= 14702623 |doi= 10.1038/nm0104-19 }}</ref>花生四烯乙醇胺在[[血漿|血漿]]中達到高峰時，發生在[[排卵期|排卵期]]，並且和[[雌二醇|雌二醇]]及[[促性腺激素|促性腺激素]]呈現[[正相關|正相關]]，這表明了以上這些物質可能參與了AEA 的調節。<ref>{{cite journal |author=El-Talatini MR, Taylor AH, Konje JC |title=The relationship between plasma levels of the endocannabinoid, anandamide, sex steroids, and gonadotrophins during the menstrual cycle |journal=Fertil. Steril. |volume=93 |issue=6 |pages=1989–96 |date=April 2010 |pmid=19200965 |doi=10.1016/j.fertnstert.2008.12.033 |last2=Taylor |last3=Konje }}</ref>而後，花生四烯乙醇胺曾被提議用來作為[[不孕症|不孕症]]的生物標誌物，但迄今為止在臨床上尚無任何預測值。<ref name="RapinoBattista2014">{{cite journal|last1=Rapino|first1=C.|last2=Battista|first2=N.|last3=Bari|first3=M.|last4=Maccarrone|first4=M.|title=Endocannabinoids as biomarkers of human reproduction|journal=Human Reproduction Update|volume=20|issue=4|year=2014|pages=501–516|issn=1355-4786|doi=10.1093/humupd/dmu004|pmid=24516083}}</ref>
花生四烯乙醇胺在[[攝食|攝食]]行為中扮演著調節的角色，而神經作用的行為以及產生愉悅的感受也受其影響。此外，將花生四烯乙醇胺直接注入大鼠的[[前腦|前腦]]正向強化刺激相關區域伏隔核時，會增強大鼠對於所攝取[[蔗糖|蔗糖]]的愉悅感，並且會增進食物的攝入量。
在1998年發表的一篇研究中也曾經提到，花生四烯乙醇胺會抑制人類[[乳腺癌細胞|乳腺癌細胞]]的增殖。<ref name="pmid9653194">{{cite journal|last1=De Petrocellis|first1=Luciano|last2=Melck|first2=Dominique|last3=Palmisano|first3=Antonella|last4=Bisogno|first4=Tiziana|last5=Laezza|first5=Chiara|last6=Bifulco|first6=Maurizio|last7=Di Marzo|first7=Vincenzo|title=The endogenous cannabinoid anandamide inhibits human breast cancer cell proliferation|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|date=7 July 1998|volume=95|issue=14|pages=8375–8380 |doi=10.1073/pnas.95.14.8375 |pmid=9653194}}</ref>
有一些研究表示，花生四烯乙醇胺的釋放為運動誘導之鎮痛作用的機制，特別是在跑步時。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.harford.de/arne/articles/NeuroReport.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-12-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131215032041/http://www.harford.de/arne/articles/NeuroReport.pdf |archivedate=2013-12-15 }}</ref>
在1996年，研究人員發現[[巧克力|巧克力]]中含有花生四烯乙醇胺。他們也發現，有兩種物質（N-oleoylethanolamine 和 N-linoleoylethanolamine）會模仿花生四烯乙醇胺帶來的影響。<ref name="pmid8751435">{{cite journal |author= di Tomaso E, Beltramo M, Piomelli D. |title= Brain cannabinoids in chocolate |journal= Nature |volume= 382 |issue= 6593 |pages= 677–8 |date=Aug 1996 |pmid= 8751435 |doi= 10.1038/382677a0|last2= Beltramo |last3= Piomelli }}</ref>

== 合成與降解 ==
人體可以由[[N-花生四烯酰磷脂酰乙醇胺|N-花生四烯酰磷脂酰乙醇胺]]（NAPE）合成花生四烯乙醇胺，而[[N-花生四烯酰磷脂酰乙醇胺|N-花生四烯酰磷脂酰乙醇胺]]（NAPE）本身是透過[[N-酰基轉移酶|N-酰基轉移酶]]，將花生四烯酸從[[卵磷脂|卵磷脂]]轉移至[[腦磷脂|腦磷脂]]上的[[游離胺|游離胺]]上。<ref name="pmid7126608">{{cite journal |author= Natarajan V, Reddy PV, Schmid PC, Schmid HH |title= N-Acylation of ethanolamine phospholipids in canine myocardium |journal= Biochim. Biophys. Acta |volume= 712 |issue= 2 |pages= 342–55 |date=August 1982 |pmid= 7126608 |doi= 10.1016/0005-2760(82)90352-6 |last2= Reddy |last3= Schmid |last4= Schmid }}</ref><ref name="pmid9006968">{{cite journal |author= Cadas H, di Tomaso E, Piomelli D |title= Occurrence and biosynthesis of endogenous cannabinoid precursor, N-arachidonoyl phosphatidylethanolamine, in rat brain |journal= J. Neurosci. |volume= 17 |issue= 4 |pages= 1226–42 |date=February 1997 |pmid= 9006968 |last2= Di Tomaso |last3= Piomelli }}</ref> 花生四烯乙醇胺由NAPE的合成可以透過多種途徑達成，包括[[酵素|酵素]]的參與，例如磷脂酶A2、磷脂酶C和NAPE-PLD<ref name=wang2009/>。
內源性花生四烯乙醇胺並不常存在且其[[半生期|半生期]]非常短，因為脂肪酸酰胺水解酶（FAAH）的作用，會將其分解成游離的花生四烯酸和乙醇胺。與仔豬相關的研究表明，花生四烯酸及其它必需脂肪酸的攝入量會影響其腦部花生四烯乙醇胺和其他內源性大麻素的量<ref name="pmid11353819">{{cite journal|last1=Berger|first1=Alvin|last2=Crozier|first2=Gayle|last3=Bisogno|first3=Tiziana|last4=Cavaliere|first4=Paolo|last5=Innis|first5=Sheila|last6=Di Marzo|first6=Vincenzo|title=Anandamide and diet: Inclusion of dietary arachidonate and docosahexaenoate leads to increased brain levels of the corresponding N-acylethanolamines in piglets|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|date=15 May 2001|volume=98|issue=11|pages=6402–6406|doi=10.1073/pnas.101119098|pmid=11353819}}</ref>。而被以高脂肪飲食飼養的小鼠，其[[肝臟|肝臟]]中的花生四烯乙醇胺的量會增加，同時也會增進[[脂肪|脂肪]]的生成<ref name="pmid15864349">{{cite journal|last1=Osei-Hyiaman|first1=Douglas|last2=DePetrillo|first2=Michael|last3=Pacher|first3=Pál|last4=Liu|first4=Jie|last5=Radaeva|first5=Svetlana|last6=Bátkai|first6=Sándor|last7=Harvey-White|first7=Judith|last8=Mackie|first8=Ken|last9=Offertáler|first9=László|last10=Wang|first10=Lei|last11=Kunos|first11=George|title=Endocannabinoid activation at hepatic CB1 receptors stimulates fatty acid synthesis and contributes to diet-induced obesity|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-clinical-investigation_2005-05_115_5/page/1298|journal=Journal of Clinical Investigation|date=2 May 2005|volume=115|issue=5|pages=1298–1305|doi=10.1172/JCI23057|pmid=15864349}}</ref>。這說明了至少在[[齧齒動物|齧齒動物]]中，花生四烯乙醇胺對於肥胖的發展會產生影響。
[[對乙酰氨基酚|對乙酰氨基酚]]（acetaminophen）在代謝上，會透過FAAH，去和花生四烯酸結合而形成AM404<ref name=AM404>{{cite journal | last=Högestätt | first=Edward D. | last2=Jönsson | first2=Bo A. G. | last3=Ermund | first3=Anna | last4=Andersson | first4=David A. | last5=Björk | first5=Henrik | last6=Alexander | first6=Jessica P. | last7=Cravatt | first7=Benjamin F. | last8=Basbaum | first8=Allan I. | last9=Zygmunt | first9=Peter M. | title=Conversion of Acetaminophen to the BioactiveN-Acylphenolamine AM404 via Fatty Acid Amide Hydrolase-dependent Arachidonic Acid Conjugation in the Nervous System | journal=Journal of Biological Chemistry | publisher=American Society for Biochemistry & Molecular Biology (ASBMB) | volume=280 | issue=36 | date=2005-06-29 | issn=0021-9258 | doi=10.1074/jbc.m501489200 | pages=31405–31412}}</ref>。此對乙酰氨基酚（acetaminophen）的代謝產物，對於[[TRPV1香草素受體|TRPV1香草素受體]]，是一種強促效劑，但對於CB1和CB2受體，為弱促效劑，而對於花生四烯乙醇胺而言，為再吸收抑制劑。因此，身體和大腦中花生四烯乙醇胺的量提升。以此方式，對乙酰氨基酚（acetaminophen）可作為仿大麻素代謝產物的[[前體藥物|前體藥物]]。這個作用可以使得對乙酰氨基酚（acetaminophen）的鎮痛作用受到部分或全部的影響<ref name="pmid17227290">{{cite journal |last1=Bertolini|first1=Alfio|last2=Ferrari|first2=Anna|last3=Ottani|first3=Alessandra|last4=Guerzoni|first4=Simona|last5=Tacchi|first5=Raffaella|last6=Leone|first6=Sheila |title=Paracetamol: New Vistas of an Old Drug |journal=CNS Drug Reviews |date=September 2006|volume=12|issue=3-4|pages=250–275 |doi=10.1111/j.1527-3458.2006.00250.x|pmid=17227290}}</ref><ref name="pmid19053765">{{cite journal |last1=Sinning|first1=Christian|last2=Watzer|first2=Bernhard|last3=Coste|first3=Ovidiu|last4=Nüsing|first4=Rolf M.|last5=Ott|first5=Ingo|last6=Ligresti|first6=Alessia|last7=Marzo|first7=Vincenzo Di|last8=Imming|first8=Peter |title=New Analgesics Synthetically Derived from the Paracetamol Metabolite-(4-Hydroxyphenyl)-(5,8,11,14)-icosatetra-5,8,11,14-enamide |journal=Journal of Medicinal Chemistry|date=25 December 2008 |volume=51|issue=24|pages=7800–7805 |doi=10.1021/jm800807k |pmid=19053765}}</ref>
。花生四烯乙醇胺和其姊妹分子2-花生四烯酸甘油酯的[[運輸蛋白|運輸蛋白]]已經被鑑定確認了，包括[[熱休克蛋白|熱休克蛋白]]（Hsp70s）和[[脂肪酸結合蛋白|脂肪酸結合蛋白]]（FABPs）。<ref name = "pnasus2009">{{cite journal |title=Identification of intracellular carriers for the endocannabinoid anandamide |year=2009 |journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America |volume=106 | issue=15 |pages=6375–6380 |last1=Kaczocha |first1=M. |last2=Glaser |first2=S.T. |last3=Deutsch |first3=D.G. |pmid=19307565 |doi=10.1073/pnas.0901515106 |pmc=2669397}}</ref><ref name = "cb2009">{{cite journal |title=Molecular identification of albumin and Hsp70 as cytosolic anandamide-binding proteins |year=2009 | journal=Chemistry & Biology |volume=16 |issue=6 |pages=624–632 |last1=Oddi | first1=S. |last2=Fezza |first2=F. |last3=Pasquariello |first3=N. | last4=D'Agostino |first4=A. |last5=Catanzaro |first5=G. |last6=De Simone | first6=C. |last7=Rapino |first7=C. |last8=Finazzi-Agro |first8=A. | last9=Maccarrone |first9=M. |pmid=19481477 | doi=10.1016/j.chembiol.2009.05.004}}</ref>

== 药用价值 ==
[[英國皇家化學學會|英國皇家化學學會]]曾表示，有研究顯示AM1172有可能被開發成藥物，可以提升大腦的花生四烯乙醇胺，用來治療焦慮以及憂鬱。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Evans|first1=Jon|title=Easing anxiety with anandamide|journal=Chemistry World|date=July 2004|url=http://www.rsc.org/chemistryworld/Issues/2004/July/anandamide.asp|access-date=2015-01-18|archive-date=2014-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141224183357/http://www.rsc.org/chemistryworld/Issues/2004/July/anandamide.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>

